## 📌 Project Overview

This project follows a real-world **data analytics pipeline** to extract actionable investment insights from stock market data:

| Stage | Tool | Task |
|-------|------|------|
| 1 | Python (Pandas, NumPy) | Data cleaning & feature engineering |
| 2 | SQL (MS SQL Server) | Business analysis — 10 queries |
| 3 | Power BI + DAX | Interactive dashboard & KPIs |
| 4 | PowerPoint | Business strategy presentation |

**Stocks Analyzed:** HDFC · Infosys · Reliance  
**Time Period:** January – December (12 months)  
**Total Trading Volume:** 233 Million units  

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

```
Python        → Pandas, NumPy, Jupyter Notebook
SQL           → MS SQL Server (10+ analytical queries, CTEs, STDEV)
Power BI      → Interactive dashboard, dynamic filters
DAX           → Calculated measures & KPI logic
PowerPoint    → Business strategy deck (11 slides)
```

